Package: ts570d-radio-control
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Matt Franklin <radiombf@gmail.com>
Section: hamradio
Priority: optional
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17)
Description: Kenwood TS-570D terminal radio control
 Terminal-based CAT control for the Kenwood TS-570D/S HF transceiver.
 Uses io_uring for low-latency serial I/O and ratatui for the TUI.
 .
 Includes:
  - ts570d-control: main control application
  - ts570d-emulator: virtual radio emulator (PTY-based, no hardware needed)
  - rs232c-pintest: RS-232C wiring/pin diagnostic tool
 .
 Requires Linux kernel 5.1+ for io_uring support.
Homepage: https://github.com/kf0uwv/ts570d
